                                <h2>About Us</h2>
                                <img class="bc-icons" src="/images/bc_icons.png" alt="Beverage Cartons Icons" width="147" height="170" />
                                <h3>Working with nature</h3>
                                <p>The Alliance for Beverage Cartons and the Environment – provides a European platform for beverage carton manufacturers and their paperboard suppliers to benchmark and profile cartons as renewable, recyclable and low carbon packaging solutions.</p>
                                <p>ACE members work together to demonstrate that beverage carton packaging is the smart green choice today and in the future.</p>
                                <a class="read-more" href="http://www.ace.be/about-ace/mission-and-identity">Read More</a>
